doc.after: The Princess Royal has her own royal banner for Canada comprising the shield of the Canadian Royal Arms defaced with a blue roundel surrounded by a wreath of gold maple leaves within which is a depiction of Princess Anne s cypher an A surmounted by a coronet and with a white label of three points the centre one charged with a red heart and the other two with red crosses taken from her coat of arms
